If you need a quick refresher on the basics of a computer vision project, take a moment to read our guide on [the key steps in a computer vision project](/guides/steps-of-a-cv-project). It will give you a solid overview of the whole process. Once you're caught up, come back here to dive into how exactly you can define and refine the goals for your project.

